Changes in VAM v1.1.0
========================

* Updated to support Seurat v5.0.0

Changes in VAM v1.0.0
========================

* Added support for gene weights.

Changes in VAM v0.5.3 
========================

* Fixed handling of gene sets with a single member.
* Fixed logic in vam() when gamma=T and center=F.

Changes in VAM v0.5.2 
========================

* Corrected conditional test for Seurat package in vignettes.

Changes in VAM v0.5.1 
========================

* Update for new SCTransform metadata structure
* Added new short SCTransform vignette

Changes in VAM v0.5.0 
========================

* Support for Seurat v4.0.0
* Moved static vignette PDFs to vignettes folder.
* Updated vamForCollection() to tolerate gene.set.collection objects specified as lists of gene ID vectors.

Changes in VAM v0.4.0 
========================

* Initial release to CRAN.
